'use strict'

// a is class and b is context
function Element (a, b) {
  this.a = a
  this.b = b
}

Element.prototype.toString = function () {
  if (!this.key) {
    this.key = this.a + this.b.toString()
  }
  return this.key
}

module.exports = Element
